  "title": "Butcher",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><p><strong>We are looking for an experienced butcher to join our team.</strong></p><p><strong>Working Hours</strong></p><ul><li><p>Morning shift only</p></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Cutting, trimming, operating machinery and preparing meat to required standards</p></li><li><p>Ensuring cleanliness and hygiene at all times</p></li><li><p>Proper handling and storage of meat</p></li><li><p>Maintaining tools and work area</p></li><li><p>Following food safety and halal handling procedures</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a butcher (mandatory)</p></li><li><p>Skilled in meat cutting and preparation</p></li><li><p>Reliable, punctual, and disciplined</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently</p></li><li><p>Physically fit for manual work</p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary</strong></p><ul><li><p>To be discussed (based on experience)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Location</strong></p><ul><li><p>To be discussed with shortlisted candidates<br />Interested candidate please contact Mr Abdul Rahman at 87531321</p></li></ul>",
